      washers, and dryers.
    </strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    Bosch appliances are known for quiet performance, modern design, and precision controls,
    but when a Bosch appliance stops working properly, accurate diagnosis matters. Many issues
    that appear simple on the surface can involve sensors, drainage systems, heating components,
    control boards, airflow problems, or temperature regulation faults.
  </p>
  <p>
    Our technicians diagnose and repair common Bosch appliance problems such as dishwashers
    that do not drain or dry correctly, refrigerators with inconsistent cooling, wall ovens
