    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Common Bosch Appliance Problems We Fix</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Bosch Dishwasher Repair:</strong>
      We fix Bosch dishwashers that are leaking, not draining, not cleaning
      properly, not drying properly, or stopping mid-cycle.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Bosch Refrigerator Repair:</strong>
      We repair Bosch refrigerators with cooling problems, temperature
      fluctuation, water leaks, frost buildup, and ice maker issues.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Bosch Oven and Range Repair:</strong>
      We service Bosch wall ovens and ranges with uneven heating, no heat,
      temperature inconsistency, display errors, and control malfunctions.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Bosch Cooktop Repair:</strong>
      We repair gas, induction, and electric cooktops with burner ignition
      problems, failed elements, sensor issues, and control faults.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Bosch Warming Drawer Repair:</strong>
      We fix warming drawers that are not heating, overheating, or not
      responding correctly to controls.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Bosch Ventilation Repair:</strong>
      We repair Bosch hoods and ventilation systems with fan problems,
      lighting failures, airflow issues, and control malfunctions.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Bosch Washer and Dryer Repair:</strong>
      We service washers with draining, spinning, and vibration issues, and
      dryers with heating, airflow, and cycle problems.
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

